ai-patthana23.56:0.2_0: under the investigation of principles means to the extent of the Dhamma.
ai-patthana23.56:0.3_0: In the past, future, and present
ai-patthana23.56:1.1_0: Not for the sake of the path, nor for the repulsion, views, etc., is the condition for the future.
ai-patthana23.56:1.1_1: This is the section in brief.
ai-patthana23.56:2.1_0: There is a group of six on sunshades and settles, and there is no unfinished when the six conditions are fulfilled.
